Introduction

Hyun Seung-hee is the Main Vocalist of the girl group OH MY GIRL under WM Entertainment. She was on Star King and Superstar K-2 and she acted in a Webdrama called 'LOSS:TIME:LIFE'.

She debuted as a member of OH MY GIRL on April 21, 2015, with the group's self-titled mini album 'Oh My Girl.

In July 2016, she competed in Girl Spirit, a singing competition show that aimed to highlight the talents of vocalists from lesser-known girl groups.
